      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JABUK (8) boasts a strong record this course with three wins and four minors from eight tries. In the money last time at Murray Bridge Straight (16.94) in a OPEN, finishing a neck third. Looks well placed and should feature. YUMALI (2) jumps from box 2 again after placing (16.98) last time at Murray Bridge Straight over 300m. Has good speed and aided by a low draw. Can measure up. SECRET SUPER (4) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (16.84) at this track behind Slick Angel in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Has good box speed and can overcome the tricky draw. Will give a great sight again. SHINY PISTOL (3) is worth including after a top-three finish most recently.",
